    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <p>Thomas G. Long was a Detroit attorney and a member of the board of directors of the Michigan Bell Telephone Company.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>The Thomas G. Long papers consist only of materials from his activities as a member of the board of directors of the Michigan Bell Telephone Company. These files pertain to telephone rate cases and to other court cases and decisions of the state's utilities commission.</p>
    </scopecontent>
